		<div class="quote"><p>@<a href="#c63927">RussellUresti</a>: Yes, I had to make the EOT. I have a blog post I'll be putting together on the matter but to sum it up: I used FontForge to convert the font to TTF and then use TTF2EOT. There are some important changes to be made in FontForge when exporting, though, to ensure that the conversion to EOT goes smoothly.
